Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=8}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:36.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I have big news! - OG}Grande notícia!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:38.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Capitão Koby escapou!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you serious?! - OG}Sério?!{Polly}
Comment: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:42.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:46.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now that he's escaped, he's no longer\NCommodore's quarry, right?! - OG}Ele escapou, então não é mais\No prêmio do comodoro, certo?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quanto vamos ganhar se capturarmos ele?!
Comment: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:50.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeehaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:54.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, não precisamos colocar recompensa nele!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:56.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Cross Guild will pay for us! - OG}A Cross Guild vai pagar pra gente!{Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu apostei nele com um bilhete de vitória!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:01.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O pagamento vai ser enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:03.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quanto vamos ganhar se matarmos ele?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're gonna be surprised! - OG}Esperem só até ouvir isso!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:09.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{His bounty is five stars! - OG}Ele vale cinco estrelas!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.82,0:02:13.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That means five treasure chests!\NThat's about 500 million berries! - OG}São cinco baús de tesouro!\NUm total de 500 milhões de berries!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.49,0:02:16.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{His bounty is five stars?! - OG}Cinco estrelas?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:18.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A captain's bounty is usually one star! - OG}Capitães normalmente só valem uma!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:24.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza! Vamos ficar ricos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:27.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The hunting begins now! - OG}Que a caçada comece!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:32.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I feel a tickle on the left side\Nof my chest-[/i1]meow[/i0]. - OG}Tô {\i1}felinamente{\i0} sentindo\Numa coceira no peito.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:36.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's where slaves are held before the sale... - OG}É ali que os escravos ficam\Nantes de serem vendidos...{Kust}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:44.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles estão fugindo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:46.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os escravos escaparam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:50.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can we hunt them all, Pizarro-san?! - OG}Podemos caçá-los, Pizarro?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't be silly! - OG}Não sejam idiotas!{Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You guys are so savage! - OG}Vocês são tão gananciosos!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:55.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tragam todos de volta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:57.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't even kill Koby! - OG}E não matem o Koby...{Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:02:59.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Or I'll tell Teach! - OG}ou eu conto pro Teach!{Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:04.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why does that rock talk?! - OG}Por que aquela montanha tá falando...?{Polly+Camo+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:06.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele sabe que estamos aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's hurry up! - OG}Vamos logo!{Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:11.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o nosso fim...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:19.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fuja antes que a gente te atrapalhe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não perca a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll be the bait... - OG}Eu vou atrair todos embora...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:28.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{so make sure you all get away! - OG}então garantam que todos escapem!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:29.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nos veremos de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, Capitão Koby...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:45.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é um santo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:58.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why don't you capture\Nthem yourself, Pizarro? - OG}Você devia ter capturado\Neles você mesmo, Pizarro.{Polly+Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:05.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then Teach will get mad at me later! - OG}{\fad(0,567)}Como eu disse, o Teach ia ficar furioso.{Polly+Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:12.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Because whenever I move, I end up breaking things-meow. - OG}Eu acabo quebrando tudo quando me {\i1}miau{\i0}xo.{Polly+CB}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:12.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:18.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can I go? - OG}Posso tentar?{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:22.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Vasco Shot, what are you gonna do-[/i1]meow[/i0]? - OG}Vasco Shot... O que {\i1}miaucê{\i0} vai fazer?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:32.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If I set the town on fire,\Nthey'll have nowhere to run. - OG}{\fad(0,485)}Eles não podem fugir se eu queimar a cidade.{Polly+Matt}
Comment: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't do that!
Comment: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:46.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That would be a huge fire-{\i1}meow{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:46.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, don't do that! That would be a huge fire-[/i1]meow[/i0]! - OG}Ei, não faz isso!\NVai ser um incêndio {\i1}miau{\i0}nstroso!{Polly+Matt+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Teach would get pissed-meow! - OG}O Teach ia ficar {\i1}furrr{\i0}ioso!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:51.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No problem. Leave it to me. - OG}Relaxa. Deixa comigo.{Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:56.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No-[/i1]meow[/i0]! We just finished\Nrepairing Rocky Port! - OG}{\i1}Purrra{\i0}! A gente acabou de reformar Rocky Port!{Kust}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:05:00.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Prefere deixar pro Wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:05.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:10.04,Main-207+,,0,0,5,,{That's out of the question-[/i1]meow[/i0]! - OG}Isso tá fora de {\i1}miaus{\i0}tão!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:13.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The whole town will be gone-[/i1]meow[/i0]! - OG}Miaucê{\i0} pode destruir\Na cidade inteira!{WF+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:18.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Encontrei ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Acho que não consigo fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:30.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I have to... - OG}De algum jeito...{Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:36.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I have to somehow keep luring them\Nuntil everyone else goes out to sea! - OG}tenho que distraí-los até\Ntodos escaparem pro mar!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.95,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Koby, o Herói!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:49.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Koby, o Herói, eu quero transformar essa ilha...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:54.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,essa Ilha dos Piratas...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:58.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,numa nação de verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:02.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma nação afiliada ao Governo Mundial!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:05.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna be the king! - OG}Vai ser o Reino do Barba Negra...{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Blackbeard Kingdom! - OG}comigo como rei!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:13.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What do you think?! - OG}O que acha?{Polly+Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:15.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's ridiculous. - OG}Para com essa besteira.{Polly+Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:17.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's no way it'd be accepted! - OG}Não tem como isso dar certo!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:20.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's a country of criminals! - OG}Seria um país de criminosos!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:24.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, don't ruin someone else's dream! - OG}Ei, não pise no sonho dos outros!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:28.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou negociar com eles\Nusando você como moeda de troca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:33.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If the government and the Marines start negotiating with terrorists, we're doomed! - OG}Se o governo ou a Marinha\Ncederem a terroristas, estamos perdidos!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:37.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And you're wasting your time. - OG}E de qualquer forma, você tá perdendo tempo.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:38.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Porque...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou membro da SWORD!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:44.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,SWORD?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:46.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que diabos é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:47.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, entendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:48.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não vai dar certo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:52.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desiste da troca, Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That means... - OG}O que ele quer dizer...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:05.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{he's a Marine but also not. - OG}é que ele é um Marine, mas também não é.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He surrendered his Marine Code. - OG}Ele entregou seu código da Marinha.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:15.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{SWORD is a group of Marines who have submitted their resignations. - OG}SWORD é um grupo de Marines que já\Nentregaram suas cartas de demissão.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:20.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So they can pick a fight with the Four Emperors without permission from above. - OG}O que significa que podem até lutar contra\Nos Quatro Imperadores sem permissão.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:24.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They can also do whatever they like and disregard any orders. - OG}Podem operar como quiserem\Ne ignorar qualquer ordem.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:25.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're wild-card commandoes! - OG}São agentes livres.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Em troca...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:32.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,a Marinha não tem nenhuma responsabilidade\Npelas ações deles...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:35.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e pode demiti-los a qualquer momento.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:43.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's the difference between the half-wits\Nwho are waiting for permission to fight us... - OG}Então tem os idiotas normais que ficam\Nesperando permissão,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:47.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and the ones who just charge in\Nwithout a care in the world! - OG}e vocês, que avançam\Nsem pensar duas vezes!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I like that style. I get it now! - OG}Agora que entendi, gosto do seu estilo!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm not gonna change my plan! - OG}Não vou mudar o plano!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:00.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll try anyway! - OG}Vou tentar mesmo assim!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:03.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even if you're a SWORD member, - OG}Mesmo sendo da SWORD,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:07.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{people call you a hero, - OG}as pessoas ainda te chamam de herói.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:11.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{so I wonder if the Marines can stick\Nto the decision of abandoning you. - OG}Será que a Marinha\Nrealmente pode te abandonar?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:14.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll ask the public! - OG}Vamos perguntar ao público!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:18.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then the government\Ncan't remain unblemished! - OG}Assim o governo não pode\Nsimplesmente lavar as mãos!{Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:24.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Até lá, tranquem ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:28.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mal posso esperar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:30.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2022)}Não deixem ele escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:35.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Volta aqui, Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:42.42,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:48.72,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll help you out, so free Moria-sama who is being held in a cell further in from here! - OG}{\t(5816,0,1,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&)}Eu te solto, mas você vai\Nlibertar o Mestre Moria da cela dele.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:51.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I cooperated with a pirate... - OG}Posso ter cooperado com um pirata...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:54.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But necessity knows no law! - OG}mas a necessidade não conhece lei!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:02.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é aquilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:15.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Three Marines showed up at the port! - OG}Três Marines apareceram no porto!{Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:18.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? Marines?! Impossível!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:20.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles são fortes! Cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:27.80,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Alguém veio me resgatar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.13,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.80,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{How arrogant I am! - OG}Que arrogante da minha parte!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.01,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{I feel ashamed! - OG}Que vergonha!{Polly+Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:52.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem são eles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que são tão fortes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles estão indo pro\Ncentro da cidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:57.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que eles querem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:00.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How would I know?! Stop them! - OG}Quem se importa?! Parem eles!{Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:08.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Armas não funcionam neles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:14.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's enough! - OG}Até aqui vocês chegam!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:19.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{His head got cut off! - OG}Cortaram a cabeça dele!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Derrubei um!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That serves you right! - OG}Bem feito!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso doeu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:35.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:36.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Logia type?! - OG}Uma logia?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's wrong with him?! - OG}Qual é a desse cara?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:41.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{His body's like clay! - OG}Parece que é feito de argila!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:45.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde você está, Koby?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ei...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Aren't those buildings moving?! - OG}Aqueles prédios estão se mexendo?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, stupid! They're not! - OG}Não, idiota! Claro que não!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:55.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você bebe demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:05.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Be a good little boy! - OG}Vai! Seja um bom menino!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:10.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Move forward! - OG}Anda logo!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:13.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There is a strange woman. Who is that? - OG}Que mulher estranha. Quem é?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:15.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Come on! Brace up! - OG}Vamos, se endireita!{Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá patético!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:22.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos! Vamos! Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:25.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela tá chicoteando um prédio...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:28.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why are you staring at me? - OG}O que foi? Tá encarando?{Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:30.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? Não, eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:33.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ela é uma Marine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:43.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How rare is it to see a marine\Nwhen you're a pirate? - OG}{\fad(0,476)}É tão raro assim pra um pirata\Nver uma Marine?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:48.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Come here. - OG}Venha aqui.{Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:50.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é tão fofinho.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll discipline you. - OG}Vou te colocar nos eixos.{Z (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:09.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tá cercado, Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.67,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, não! Tô cercado!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mirem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:21.55,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is it for me! - OG}Esse é o meu fim?{Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shoot all at once! - OG}Ao meu sinal!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:26.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:38.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:40.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:43.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:56.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É lindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:57.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que diabos é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que saiu uma flor do cano?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, espera...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:05.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:11.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{something that Dr. Vegapunk invented... - OG}uma das invenções do Dr. Vegapunk!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:18.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{which earned him the Mobel Peace Prize! - OG}Rendeu a ele o Prêmio Mobel da Paz!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é isso que eu tô perguntando!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem fez isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:26.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Koby{-senpai}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:31.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vem pra cá!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:32.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não quis dizer nada estranho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:41.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hibari-san! Why are you here?! - OG}Hibari! O que você tá fazendo aqui?!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:42.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não me diz que...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:43.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right! - OG}Isso!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:47.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I shot flower rounds, the flowers\Nthat bloom out of gunpowder! - OG}Eu atirei balas de flores,\Nque fazem a pólvora florescer!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:50.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The enemies can't use their weapons! - OG}Eles não podem usar suas armas!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:51.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get away quickly while you can! - OG}Fujam enquanto podem!{Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:54.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-E...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:56.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,se você estiver com fome, eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,fiz...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{bento for you! - OG}uma marmita pra você!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What? - OG}Hein?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,107)}Não, quer dizer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:13.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Prince! Algum progresso?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, our task has just been completed. - OG}Sim, acabamos de terminar aqui.{Polly+Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:27.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Koby is okay, too! - OG}{\an1}O Koby também tá a salvo!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:34.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{H-Hey... Has this open area\Nalways been shaped like this? - OG}E-Ei... Essa praça sempre\Nteve esse formato?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:34.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:40.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele prédio não tá se mexendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ei, espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:46.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A-Ah, não...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:48.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não dá pra sair daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, quando estiverem prontos!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Come to the dead center! - OG}Vão pro centro!{Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:55.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Consegui contatar o Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:57.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá tudo pronto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vice-Almirante Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:02.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo, se segurem em algo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:07.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ao ataque!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:17.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos! Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:19.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos sair daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olhem pra cima!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quêêê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:40.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quêêê?!\N– O quêêê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:44.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A Marine ship is flying up there! - OG}Um navio da Marinha tá voando no céu!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:47.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why?! How's that possible?! - OG}Por quê?! Como é possível?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem tá nele?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:52.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele não tá... caindo na nossa direção?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:55.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,C-Corre!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olhem!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:07.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Impossível! Achei que ele tinha se aposentado!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:09.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O lendário...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:11.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Herói!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:19.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vice-Almirante Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vim te salvar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:28.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Corre! Só corre!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não dá...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tem saída!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:38.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, seus piratas malditos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:41.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tá vindo! Corre!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:01.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vice-Almirante Garp...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:05.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why? I'm not worthy enough to save... - OG}Por quê? Eu nem valho a pena salvar...{Z+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:07.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You fools! - OG}Seus idiotas!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:13.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who do you think you have kidnapped?! - OG}Vocês fazem ideia de quem\Nvocês sequestraram?!{Polly+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:25.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Koby é o futuro da Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:29.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And... - OG}Sem falar...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:33.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{he's also my beloved pupil! - OG}no meu querido protegido!{Polly+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:38.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:53.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:54.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Cumulo-glorpus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn Garp! - OG}Maldito Garp!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:11.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele é maluco!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:13.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou fazer esse velho pagar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:15.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't move, you pirates! - OG}Não se mexam, piratas!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:19.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Resistance will result in further damage! - OG}Resistência só vai resultar em mais danos!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:29.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm not satisfied... - OG}Patético demais...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:32.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm off my game. - OG}Realmente enferrujei.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:34.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai se ferrar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:36.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We can't take any more damage! - OG}Como se tivesse sobrado algo pra destruir!{Kust}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:39.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vice-Almirante Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tá bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:49.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm so relieved! - OG}Graças a Deus!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He didn't get killed! - OG}Eles não mataram ele!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Gee... - OG}Francamente...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele exagerou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:57.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Garp is a bad boy! - OG}Você é muito levado, Garp!{Polly+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:20:01.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Garp - -san}{said Koby's the future of\Nthe Marines. It's unforgivable! - OG}O Garp disse que o Koby é o futuro da\NMarinha. Não vou aceitar isso!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll drag him down! - OG}Vou sabotá-lo!{Z (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:08.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You've got to do those things\Nin secret, you spoiled brat. - OG}Isso é coisa que se faz\Nem segredo, mimada.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:09.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So cute. - OG}Assim fica mais fofo.{Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:11.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:14.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capitão Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Koby{-kun}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:18.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tashigi{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:21.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even those who are not SWORD members... - OG}Até quem não é da SWORD veio...{Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:25.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why are you carrying that, Koby? - OG}Ei, Koby! Por que tá\Ncarregando essa coisa?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:26.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vice-Almirante Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:30.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We can't get the shackle removed\Nand we didn't know what to do! - OG}Tentamos de tudo,\Nmas não conseguimos tirar a algema!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,faça...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:37.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,algu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:39.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,coisa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:46.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hibari{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:51.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hibari{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:04.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kuzan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:06.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kuzan{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:08.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você tá fazendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.04,0:21:10.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Thaw out Hibari-san! - OG}Descongele ela agora!{Polly+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:14.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's Aokiji! - OG}É o Aokiji!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:17.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capitão Kuzan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:19.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kuzan{-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:22.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't get me into trouble, Koby. - OG}Não me arrume problemas, Koby.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:24.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não posso deixar você fugir...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:27.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,enquanto o Teach tá fora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:33.90,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Two years ago, over the position of\Nthe Marine Headquarters' next Fleet Admiral, - OG}Dois anos atrás, os Almirantes Akainu e Aokiji...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:40.57,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{a big fight erupted between\NAdmiral Akainu and Admiral Aokiji. - OG}lutaram pela posição do próximo\Nalmirante de frota do Quartel-General.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:49.08,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{After 10 days of a deadly struggle,\Nthe victory went to... - OG}A luta mortal durou dez dias\Naté surgir um vencedor:{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:50.79,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Akainu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:57.09,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{However, Aokiji refused to serve under Akainu. - OG}Porém, Aokiji se recusou a servir sob ele.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:21:59.46,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{And he left the Navy. - OG}E então, deixou a Marinha.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:21.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que droga é essa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.78,0:22:23.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Barba Negra tá aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:26.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Corre! Sai da cidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.37,0:22:27.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:29.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:32.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera! Quem fez isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.59,0:22:39.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, não preciso perguntar...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:45.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There is only one person\Nin the world who can do this! - OG}Só tem uma pessoa\Nno mundo que poderia ter feito isso!{Yag+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:49.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Foi você!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:51.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aokiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:06.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Minha tripulação tá congelada lá fora!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:08.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desfaz isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:12.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tá me irritando.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:16.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You better not use your\NQuake-Quake Fruit power. - OG}E nem pense em usar seu poder.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:19.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They'll shatter and die. - OG}Sua tripulação vai se despedaçar e morrer.{Polly+Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.30,0:23:24.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é o capitão deles, então acho que sabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:28.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you think I started it? - OG}Acha mesmo que fui eu que comecei?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:31.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And you also know what happened\Nto me, don't you? - OG}Aliás, você já sabe, não sabe?{Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:36.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm brokenhearted and angry. - OG}Não tô só de coração partido, tô furioso.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.94,0:23:41.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So imagine whose fault it actually is. - OG}Tenta adivinhar quem realmente começou isso.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.67,0:24:08.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We need more booze! - OG}Mais uma rodada aqui!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:12.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're quite the drinker, Ice Pop! - OG}Você aguenta bem a bebida, Picolé!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.93,0:24:15.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You too, you scummy son of a bitch! - OG}Você também, seu desgraçado!{Matt+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.14,0:24:21.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And what did Akainu say? - OG}E o que o Akainu disse depois?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.90,0:24:28.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{"We enlisted the same year\Nand are now in a deadly battle. - OG}"Dois homens que se alistaram no mesmo ano\Nnuma luta de morte...{Polly (Viz-ish)}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.03,0:24:31.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I feel a hot lump in my throat." - OG}Meus olhos estão ardendo de lágrimas."{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.95,0:24:34.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, that's because... - OG}E eu disse: "É, isso é por que...{Z+Polly}
Comment: 0,0:24:31.95,0:24:33.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's because...
Comment: 0,0:24:33.28,0:24:34.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.29,0:24:38.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{you're magma! - OG}seu magma tá escorrendo!"{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.17,0:24:41.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Because of that, look! - OG}E agora olha!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.59,0:24:47.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm one-legged now! - OG}Fiquei com uma perna só!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.47,0:24:51.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É isso que acontece\Nquando dois almirantes lutam!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.43,0:24:52.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E o Akainu?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.51,0:24:55.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Did you at least pull one of his arms off?! - OG}Pelo menos arrancou um braço dele?!{Yag}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.27,0:24:57.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.98,0:25:02.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But I'm sure he's covered in scars. - OG}Mas tenho certeza que ele tá cheio de cicatrizes.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.19,0:25:09.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Speaking of scars, he might know\Nthe Man with the Burn Scar, Commodore. - OG}Falando em cicatrizes, ele pode conhecer\No Cicatriz de Queimadura, Comodoro.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.90,0:25:12.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Huh? The Man with the Burn Scar? - OG}Hein? Cicatriz de Queimadura?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.03,0:25:17.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Existem quatro lode poneglyphs\Nimportantes no mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.96,0:25:24.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And it seems like Kaido\Nand Big Mom have one each... - OG}Big Mom e Kaido têm dois deles...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.25,0:25:30.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas não conseguimos encontrar os outros dois!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.59,0:25:33.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's another example of fate... - OG}Mais uma vez o destino interfere...{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.34,0:25:34.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.30,0:25:40.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E dizem que o Homem com a\NCicatriz de Queimadura tem um deles.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.02,0:25:43.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Maybe that's me. - OG}Será que sou eu?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.19,0:25:45.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You just got that scar recently! - OG}Você acabou de ganhar essa cicatriz, idiota!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.24,0:25:52.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Rumor has it that... - OG}Dizem que...{Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.54,0:26:03.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{that man sails a pitch-black ship... - OG}ele navega num navio totalmente negro.{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.34,0:26:16.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And if someone approaches, he'll create\Na giant whirlpool which swallows you up. - OG}E quando alguém chega perto, ele cria\Num redemoinho gigante que engole tudo.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.85,0:26:23.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He might be a devil fruit power user... - OG}Ele pode ter comido uma fruta do diabo...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.19,0:26:27.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acredito que ele trabalha pro governo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.27,0:26:31.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In fact, the World Government\Nhas a deep dark side. - OG}O Governo Mundial tem\Nsegredos sombrios, afinal.{Polly (Viz-ish)}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.82,0:26:34.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If they just hold on to one of the stones, - OG}Se mantiverem ao menos uma das pedras,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.70,0:26:43.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{that'll help prevent pirates from reaching\Nthe great treasure of the One Piece... - OG}nenhum pirata jamais alcançará o\NOne Piece, o maior tesouro escondido.{Polly+Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.75,0:26:48.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The poneglyphs... I only have\Nbitter memories with them. - OG}Os poneglyphs... só tenho\Nlembranças amargas deles.{Polly+Z+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.63,0:26:54.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If I had seen such an eye-catching\Nred stone in Ohara, I would remember it. - OG}Se eu tivesse visto uma pedra vermelha\Nassim em Ohara, eu lembraria.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.93,0:26:58.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All I remember... - OG}Tudo que eu lembro...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.05,0:27:01.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{is my best friend who rebelled\Nagainst the government... - OG}é um bom amigo que se rebelou\Ncontra o governo...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.31,0:27:04.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and the sad-looking eyes of a girl... - OG}e uma garota com olhos cheios de desespero...{Polly+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.64,0:27:08.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,cujo destino estava nas minhas mãos.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.73,0:27:13.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What kind of a dull story is that?! - OG}Que história chata é essa?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.45,0:27:18.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Comodoro, o que fazemos?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.66,0:27:19.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.66,0:27:24.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se tomarmos o poder dele pra nós,\Nvai ser um grande trunfo...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.46,0:27:32.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I heard that, you pieces of shit! - OG}Eu ouvi, seus desgraçados!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.63,0:27:38.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you all wanna go to the world of ice?! - OG}Querem que eu mande vocês pro inferno gelado?!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.14,0:27:43.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Para, para, para!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.06,0:27:50.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh yeah, I heard that you guys\Nwere hunting devil fruit power users. - OG}Ah é, já ouvi que vocês\Nandam caçando poderes de frutas do diabo.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.28,0:27:54.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pode vir!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.66,0:28:00.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.74,0:28:02.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me desculpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.99,0:28:05.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que meu tripulante disse foi ridículo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.37,0:28:08.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wasn't gonna do that. - OG}Eu jamais faria algo assim.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.92,0:28:11.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I rather wanted to ask you... - OG}O que eu realmente queria te perguntar é...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.04,0:28:13.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you wanna come aboard my ship? - OG}Quer navegar com a gente?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.46,0:28:17.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What? Captain, are you crazy?! - OG}O quê?! Capitão, pirou?!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.72,0:28:20.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're unemployed now, aren't you? - OG}Você perdeu seu cargo, não perdeu?{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.68,0:28:22.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem algum lugar pra ir?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.68,0:28:24.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que vai fazer agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.68,0:28:27.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{After getting thrown out\Nby the guardians of justice. - OG}Os guardiões da justiça te abandonaram!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.14,0:28:30.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've sunk so low that a pirate\Nis worried about my employment. - OG}Cara, isso deve ser o fundo do poço.{WF+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.27,0:28:34.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've sunk so low that a pirate\Nis worried about my employment. - OG}Um pirata preocupado com meu futuro.{WF+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.15,0:28:37.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra onde quer que vá, o que quer que faça,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.99,0:28:41.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{you'll always get involved\Nin some kind of strife! - OG}os problemas sempre vão te encontrar!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.12,0:28:46.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então sob qual bandeira você vai lutar?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.29,0:28:47.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.08,0:28:52.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm different from the people in the Navy! - OG}Eu sou diferente dos Marines!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.09,0:28:54.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{My brand of justice is different from theirs! - OG}Eu tenho minha própria justiça!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.92,0:28:56.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't be silly! - OG}Não seja idiota!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.26,0:29:01.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How can I trust vermin like you guys\Njust after a few drinks together?! - OG}Só porque bebemos juntos\Nnão quer dizer que confio em escória como vocês!{Polly+Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.26,0:29:02.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Epa, epa!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.64,0:29:05.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I think you misunderstand what pirates are. - OG}Acho que você entendeu errado o que são piratas.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.52,0:29:09.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're not a group of good friends! - OG}Não é como se fôssemos todos amiguinhos!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.69,0:29:16.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{For a pirate group... - OG}A única coisa que uma tripulação pirata precisa...{Yag}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.57,0:29:23.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{all that matters is that\Nwe share mutual interests! - OG}é ter interesses em comum!{Polly+Yag}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.62,0:29:29.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora você é livre...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.25,0:29:33.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What do you want to do? - OG}então o que quer fazer?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.72,0:29:49.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Kuzan!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.81,0:29:51.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Descongela a Hibari!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.19,0:29:53.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Allow Koby to escape! - OG}Deixa o Koby escapar!{Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.98,0:29:56.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Volta pra Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.44,0:30:04.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You haven't changed.\NYou say whatever you wish. - OG}Você não mudou nada.\NSempre falando o que pensa.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.29,0:30:12.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't let any of that happen, Garp-san! - OG}Mas não posso fazer nada disso, Garp!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.29,0:30:15.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I really like... - OG}Eu sempre admirei...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.96,0:30:17.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,o quanto você é direto...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.42,0:30:22.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{so I'm living the way I want to now! - OG}por isso agora tô vivendo do {\i1}meu{\i0} jeito!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.93,0:30:29.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Idiot... - OG}Cabeça-dura...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.03,0:30:46.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}Ice...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.37,0:30:48.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.83,0:30:56.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vice-Almirante Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.96,0:31:00.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vice-Almirante Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.26,0:31:06.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In order to save your beloved pupil, - OG}Pra salvar seu querido protegido,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.47,0:31:11.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{can you kill your pupil from the past?! - OG}consegue matar seu antigo discípulo?!{Polly+Matt}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.68,0:31:15.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't live in the past, you idiot! - OG}Não viva no passado, seu idiota!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.52,0:31:20.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu te ensinei a viver o presente!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.16,0:31:27.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não funcionou!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.47,0:31:49.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Escuta, Kuzan!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.41,0:32:14.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Those who waver... - OG}Hesitar é sinal...{Polly (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.37,0:32:17.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{are weak! - OG}de fraqueza!{Polly (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.54,0:32:22.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Blue Hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.95,0:32:55.66,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Enquanto isso, na Ilha Winner...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.45,0:33:37.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Since you lost your ship,\Nyou're no longer a pirate group! - OG}Sem navio, vocês mal podem\Nse chamar de tripulação pirata!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.83,0:33:40.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You have no means of escape, either! - OG}Não tem como escapar!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.17,0:33:47.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The 100 pirates who got their hearts\Nstolen by you at Rocky Port... - OG}Os cem piratas cujos corações\Nvocê roubou em Rocky Port...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.42,0:33:52.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,ainda vivem com medo na Ilha dos Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.39,0:33:58.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If I bring back your heart,\Nthey'll make a toast in joy! - OG}Mas se eu levar o {\i1}seu{\i0} coração,\Nvão brindar de alegria!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.48,0:34:07.73,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Você realmente fez pra mim!{faux flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.73,0:34:11.70,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(3479,0,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Mas não garanto que vá funcionar.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.45,0:34:19.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.08,0:34:23.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tô em dúvida se vendo\Nou uso a Ope Ope no Mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.46,0:34:26.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It can even grant me\Nperpetual youth, can't it?! - OG}Ela até pode me dar juventude eterna, não pode?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.43,0:34:37.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Leave Captain... - OG}Tire as mãos...{Polly (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.31,0:34:41.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{alone! - OG}do meu capitão!{Polly (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.78,0:34:51.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bepo...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.78,0:34:59.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Sulong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.91,0:35:02.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Impossível! Nem tem lua!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.92,0:35:13.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera, espera, espera, espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.23,0:35:31.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capitão!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.09,0:35:55.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn! He fled to the sea! - OG}Droga! Eles fugiram pro mar!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.38,0:35:57.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não deixem ele escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.56,0:36:07.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Volta, Bepo...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.61,0:36:15.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't... leave my friends... behind... - OG}Não posso... deixar a tripulação... pra trás...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.90,0:36:17.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, I won't! - OG}Eu não volto!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.41,0:36:20.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Confia neles, Capitão!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.78,0:36:23.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{From the extremely cold port\Nof the north till now... - OG}Daquele porto gelado do norte\Naté agora...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.58,0:36:28.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,sempre sobrevivemos!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.96,0:36:30.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.54,0:36:34.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,nenhum de nós vai morrer aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.80,0:36:42.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já superamos tanta coisa juntos!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.64,0:36:46.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, Capitão!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.60,0:36:50.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não morra!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.95,0:37:00.53,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.91,0:37:03.91,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,não morra!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.12,0:37:12.84,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Na Ilha Winner, no Novo Mundo...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.39,0:37:26.10,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,o submarino dos Piratas do Heart, o {\i0}Polar Tang{\i1},
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.47,0:37:27.98,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{sank. - OG}foi afundado.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.44,0:37:35.61,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Os Piratas do Heart, liderados por Trafalgar Law...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.82,0:37:38.32,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,foram derrotados.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=9}===============================DIALOGUE============================
